{[%evp 0,3,60,59,77,46] [#]} {Black has just played 9...Nh5 - where will you
go with the bishop and why?} 10. Be3 $1 {[%csl Rh5] In general it's not a good
idea to allow this bishop to be traded by a knight - here the knight on h5
feels misplaced.} (10. Bg3 $6 {of course, is possible but White loses a great
deal of control in the center.} Nxg3 11. hxg3 g6 {[%cal Re7f6,Rf6g7]}) 10...
Qc7 {[%cal Rh5f4]} 11. g3 $1 {[%cal Gf3e5] and the black knight is pushed away.
} *

