{[#]} {What idea here for White is important to know?} 13. g4 $5 {this can
lead to a very sharp and spectacular game.} Ne3 {accepting the thrown gauntlet}
(13... Nd6 {feels more careful.}) 14. Bxh7+ $1 Kxh7 15. Qh4+ Kg8 16. Rf3 {
[%csl Rg8][%cal Gf3h3,Gf3e3] and White develops a very dangerous initiative.} *

