[SourceVersionDate "2018.11.06"]

{[%cal Rh5h4] [#]} {Black has just castled long, intending to develop an
initiative at the kingside with h5-h4. What should you do?} 13. a4 $1 {At your
disposal is a very simple, yet strong plan - push forward the a-pawn as far as
possible, even if you have to sacrifice it. White's attack is faster.} Kb8 (
13... h4 14. Nxh4 Rxh4 15. gxh4 Rh8 16. Bg5 Bxh2+ 17. Kg2 $16 {[%cal Gf1h1]
shouldn't really bother White.}) 14. a5 Nxa5 15. Bg5 {[%cal Ga1a4,Gf1a1] with
a very dangerous initiative.} *

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
